==English==
===Etymology===

When the [[Portuguese]] discovered Taiwan, they named it ''Formosa'', which means ''beautiful''.

===Proper noun===
'''Formosa'''

# The name given to the province of [[Taiwan]] by the [[Portuguese]] colonist in the 16th century.

